data.description: 2 bedroom + bonus room home with private gated beach access is now available for purchase in the coastal Beachcrest neighborhood of Olympia. Set back off the Nisqually Reach & South Sound waterway, this charming community is a perfect place to put down roots! Front porch & entry of home open into a light-filled family room. Family-room guides you into the kitchen w/ eating space & dining room. Sliding glass door leading to the back yard, complete with deck & mature landscaping! Upstairs leads to spacious bedrooms to call your own. Community is surrounded by Hawks Prairie Golf Course to the SW, waterfront to the North, Tolmie State Park to the NW, & Billy Frank Nisqually National Wildlife Park SE. What memories will you make living here?
